title: Vaults of Terra - (Space Marine) Chapters - Raven Guard - Culture, Organisation and Equipment
description:
The Vaults of Terra bring you the second and final raven guard video describing their tactics, organisation and some of their equipment choices.

Voting is still open for Space Marine chapters; please vote in the comments below to see your favorite chapter up next.

Vaults of Terra Intro:
Stealth Shock

Intro Music: 
Daniel Yount - Dark Times
